@startuml WorkoutPlanActivityDiagram
|Trainer|
start
:Select assigned Member;
:Create Workout Plan;
:Define Goal & Duration;
|System|
:Validate Trainer Assignment;
if (Not Assigned?) then (yes)
  :Deny Access;
  |Trainer|
  stop
else (no)
  |Trainer|
  :Add Exercises (Sets/Reps);
  |System|
  :Save Workout Plan to DB;
  :Link Exercises to Plan;
  |Member|
  :Receive Notification/View;
  :Execute Plan;
  :Update Metrics/Progress;
  |System|
  :Record Progress;
endif
stop
@enduml
